title: Nintendo Kirby Collection (English)
description:
Nintendo Kirby Collection
Uploaded by _Firefly on thepiratebay.org

------------------------------

Includes:

(In order of release)

MAIN SERIES:

- Kirby's Dream Land (Gameboy)
- Kirby's Adventure (NES)
- Kirby's Dream Land 2 (Gameboy)
- Kirby's Super Star (SNES)
- Kirby's Dream Land 3 (SNES)
- Kirby 64 - The Crystal Shards (N64)
- Kirby & The Amazing Mirror (GBA)
- Kirby: Squeak Squad (DS)
- Kirby's Adventure/Kirby's Return to Dream Land (Wii)

SPIN-OFFS:

- Kirby's Pinball Land (Gameboy)
- Kirby's Dream course (SNES)
- Kirby's Avalanche (SNES)
- Kirby's Block Ball (Gameboy)
- Kirby's Star Stacker (Gameboy)
- Kirby's Tilt 'n Tumble (Gameboy Color)
- Kirby Air Ride (Gamecube)
- Kirby's Epic Yarn (Wii)
- Kirby Mass Attack (DS)

REMAKES & COLLECTIONS:

- Kirby: Nightmare In Dream Land (GBA)
- Kirby Super Star Ultra (DS)
- Kirby's Dream Collection - Special Edition (Wii)

CURSE SERIES:

- Kirby: Canvas Curse (DS)

ALSO INCLUDES EMULATORS FOR EACH SYSTEM

------------------------------

Important Info:

The only games missing from this collection are Kirby: Triple Deluxe, Kirby: Planet Robobot and Kirby and the Rainbow Curse.
These games are missing since they are 3DS and Wii U titles, making them more difficult to emulate. You'd be best off buying them.

All these games are neatly organised in different folders and numbered by order of release.

Also included is many emulators for each system, packed into seperate folders so you know what they are.

Thanks for reading and have fun! PLEASE SEED! (I can't do it alone!)

Uploaded by _Firefly on thepiratebay.org

------------------------------
